0xE0BA9FE6// GetVehicleWheelTireColliderSize
float GET_VEHICLE_WHEEL_TIRE_COLLIDER_SIZE(Vehicle vehicle, int wheelIndex);Parameters:vehicle: The vehicle to obtain data for.wheelIndex: Index of wheel, 0-3.Returns: Float representing size of the wheel collider.
